title: Will Arnett / MCL Tear and Cold Plunging
description: In our first episode ever, Sean and Dr. Wali discuss his nose job gone wrong. Will Arnett joins us to discuss his MCL tear and his love of the sauna and cold plunging. The guys go head to head against each other in some epic medical trivia!
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
